<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5078] RestartResponseException broken with page instance and bookmarkable page</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5078</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If I do throw new RestartResponseException(new OtherPage(&quot;redirected!&quot;)); on OtherPage itself and OtherPage is mounted then a completely new page is constructed and displayed instead of the instance I created.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Does not happen if the page isn&apos;t mounted or the current page is not OtherPage. If I hide the default constructor it also doesn&apos;t happen.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll attach a quickstart which demonstrates the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
